
Samba::DB: perl Samba log parser and SQLite record database

Requires DBD::SQLite.

Interprets Samba log records (e.g. synthesizes sessions from raw data)
and loads into a simple SQLite database table.

installation:

  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make install

usage:

  smbdb : actual application; run with no arguments for synopsys
  smbdmp : low-level log dump
  smbproc : higher-level 'event' dump
  loadsmbdir : wrapper to load directory-of-logs as is common/default config

